OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry day for many with sunny
OL,6,Fspells, though the cloud may be thick
OL,7,Fenough to give the odd light shower,
OL,8,Fespecially during the morning in the
OL,9,Fsouth. Feeling a little fresher than
OL,10,FMonday.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely dry overnight with a
OL,13,Fmix of cloud and clear spells. Turning
OL,14,Fchilly in any prolonged clear spells,
OL,15,Fwith perhaps some patchy mist and fog
OL,16,Fdeveloping.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
