OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FDry on Wednesday with a mix
OL,6,Fof cloud and sunny spells. Sunshine
OL,7,Ftending to increase throughout the
OL,8,Fafternoon, and with lighter winds it
OL,9,Fbegin to feel warmer.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FLargely dry and bright on Thursday,
OL,13,Fbut rain arriving later. High pressure
OL,14,Fbuilds back in from Friday bringing
OL,15,Fplenty of dry and bright weather, but
OL,16,Ftemperatures returning to nearer
OL,17,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
